It was dark, chilly, moonless night and I was snoring CONTENTEDLY under my cozy comforter.
I was having the most FABUMOUSE dream! In my Dream I was floating in space, happily hovering over
cream cake asteriods, Italian cheese pizza planets, and Coco Cola volcanic comets...
Just as I was about to NIBBLE on a yummy looking pepperoni crater, something woke me up.
I heard Cling Cling Cling from my alarm. It was 9:00 clock in the morning and then I had rememberd 
it was a Sunday. I had offed the alarm and I went to sleep to explore the planets
